data.description:
Discover the epitome of tranquility in this 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom residence located in the highly desirable Pass Christian area. Nestled on a generous plot of nearly 2 acres, this property offers a myriad of possibilities for creating your own idyllic backyard oasis.

Step inside to experience the open-concept living area that bathes in natural light, creating a seamless connection with the surrounding beauty of the outdoors.

The master bedroom provides a serene retreat, complete with an ensuite bathroom for added privacy and relaxation. Two additional bedrooms cater to versatile needs, whether accommodating family, guests, or a dedicated home office.

The true allure of this property lies in its sprawling backyard canvas, where your imagination can run wild. With ample space to spare, the potential for lush gardens, recreational areas, or a luxurious pool awaits your personal touch.

Benefit from this enviable location, renowned for its award-winning schools, ensuring an exceptional educational experience for your family.

Embrace the allure of Pass Christian living and seize the opportunity to make this home your own. Schedule a private tour today and explore the possibilities that await in this exquisite property. Don't delay, as this remarkable opportunity won't stay available for long.
**Professional Photos Coming Soon!**
